<item>
            <title>[DERBY-6221] Can&apos;t select from SYS.SYSUSERS if you use a WHERE clause in the query</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6221</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following query runs fine:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;SELECT username, lastmodified FROM sys.sysusers;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;...but the following query raises an exception:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;SELECT username, lastmodified FROM sys.sysusers WHERE USERNAME = &apos;FRED&apos;;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;...which is&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ERROR 4251E: No one can view the &apos;SYSUSERS&apos;.&apos;PASSWORD&apos; column.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
